[63]NPR Music's Tiny Desk Concerts and globalFEST Return for 2025 Edition

   [64]March 31, 2025 

[65]Statement of Katherine Maher President and CEO, National Public Radio

   [66]March 26, 2025  March 26, 2025; Washington, D.C. – This morning,
   NPR President & CEO Katherine Maher and PBS President & CEO Paula
   Kerger will appear as witnesses at a hearing called by the House
   Delivering on Government Efficiency (DOGE) Subcommittee.

[67]NPR Music's "Tiny Desk Radio" show debuts on radio stations nationwide
April 17

   [68]March 17, 2025 

   Sponsor Message

[69]It's Been a Minute with Brittany Luse and Wild Card with Rachel Martin
launch as hour-long radio program

   [70]March 6, 2025  The two shows can now be heard as an hour-long
   radio program on Member stations around the country.

[71]NPR Board Elects Stephen George as Public Director

   [72]February 20, 2025  NPR welcomes the election of Stephen George to
   the NPR Board of Directors as a Public Director.

   [73]Alternate Realities is a new limited series from NPR's Embedded.

